Description:
To a Tee at Aqui
Brilliant North West facing apartment nestled in the Aqui Promenade residential complex, designed by award winning architects Woods Bagot.
Located on the 10th floor, this spacious 1 bedroom has so much to offer.
Open plan dining and living area adjoins a fantastic undercover balcony perfect for relaxing.
Modern galley kitchen with integrated stainless steel Miele appliances including gas stove top and oven. Plenty of storage space highlighted by a maroon feature panel.
Stylish bedroom with mirrored built in robes, also with floor to ceiling windows.
Fully tiled bathroom with maroon coloured tiled feature wall matching the scheme of the kitchen.
Other features include: Split system air conditioner, floorboards in the main traffic area and carpeted bedroom, modern black tapware, timber veneer detailing, and stone benchtops.
Complex features include: 25m swimming pool, gymnasium, onsite manager, security entrance, business/study meeting area, communal BBQ and landscaped rooftop garden.
Located close to District Docklands shopping precinct, new Hoyts Cinema, O'Brien ice rink and Ron Barassi Snr park. Free tram zoned, close to Southern Cross Station, and easy access to the freeway system.
Invest now and move in later!
Call Eugene Louey on 0401 299 997.

Description:
Stunning 15th Floor Gem
Making a genuine statement with memorable views of the marina and CBD, luxury modern style, and a place in the desired Yarras Edge precinct. This sophisticated two bedroom, two bathroom apartment will impress all!
Enjoying bright floor-to-ceiling windows, stone benchtops, quality fittings and fixtures, and a thoughtful layout, this inspired dwelling will have widespread appeal. The generous lounge and dining space flows out to a charmed undercover balcony which is the ideal spot to soak in the brilliant city and Yarra River vistas, meanwhile back inside and the kitchen has everything you need including a gleaming glass splashback, stone island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances.
Both bedrooms come complete with built-in robes including the master bedroom which features a pristine double vanity ensuite, while other features include a central bathroom, European laundry, ducted heat/cool, video intercom, and one secure car space. You also have direct park frontage to complete this amazing package!
The Yarras Point building sits in a peaceful yet convenient part of the Yarras Edge precinct, which is close to South Wharf Promenade delivering excellent restaurants and bars incluidng The General Assembly, Charlie Lovett, Munich Brauhaus and The Boatbuilders Yard. Youre also a short walk to the DFO shopping, CBD and Southbank attractions, Crown Casino, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Docklands would have to be one of Melbournes most dynamic and evolving suburbs. With key attractions including Marvel Stadium and the Melbourne Star. A modern building that features security access entry and resort style facilities including an outdoor swimming pool and a fully equipped gym for resident use.

Description:
Enjoy a Heritage Life Style
Within the "Grand Central Apartments" one of Melbourne's most historic buildings this two bedroom apartment provides a secure city lifestyle opportunity where you are welcomed by lofty arches and a superb imperial staircase as you enter the main central foyer of this magnificent building.
Positioned on the fourth floor and spread over two levels with classic features, plush carpets and high double glazed windows. Comprises entry hall through to a comfortably proportioned living and dining zone with plenty of natural light, an adjoining well appointed kitchen with quality Blanco appliances including dishwasher, a powder room with laundry facilities. The upper mezzanine level includes two bedrooms both with built in robes and a central bathroom. Other features include heating, cooling, intercom entry, lift access and a car parking space on title.
Residents have use of the buildings pool, spa, gym, sauna and BBQ area.
Perfectly located to transport, trams, Southern Cross Station, Collins Street, Crown Casino, Etihad Stadium, Docklands precinct plus an abundance of dining and shopping options all close by.

Sub-penthouse guaranteeing renovated luxury and stellar views
Stunningly refurbished to include luxurious and designer finishes, which is only matched by the breathtaking 28th floor views of the CBD, northern mountain ranges, and Port Phillip Bay, this exquisite 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom sub-penthouse is the ultimate Yarras Edge prize. Being a resident of this terrific complex also gives you access to RekDek including a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Brilliant new features include engineered oak flooring and 70 ounce plush wool carpet
Fantastic wraparound balcony promises views to the north plus the Yarra River and iconic city skyline

Comfort, Convenience and Contemporary Class
Taking in a spectacular north-facing aspect in the south tower of the affluent Watergate residential complex, this spacious and simply stunning apartment was built for a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and contemporary class.
On the doorstep of the abundance of shopping, entertainment and transport options associated with the incredible Docklands quarter, this spectacular dwelling is spread over approximately 108sqm of modern style and high-end finishes.

WATERFRONT TOWNHOUSE
Over 220SQM in size plus a huge Terrace with water views from every room. Situated on the North / West corner of the near new Array complex in the heart of the prestigious Yarra's Edge, this stunning double storey ground floor podium townhouse offers peaceful uninterrupted views of the marina and park.
The property offers expansive open plan living and dining area complimented by an abundance of natural light and floor to ceiling windows leading to your very own private wrap around terrace.
Indulge in a smartly designed gourmet kitchen perfect for the entertainer, fitted with an island benchtop, complimented with the finest fittings and finishes including, stone benchtops, Miele appliances and ample cupboard space.

Unique in its design, providing all the comforts of a home, this elite waterfront property has its own private access and is designed for those looking for quality and luxury combined with the exciting lifestyle of the Docklands.
This is a must inspect and is sure to impress.

Description:
Fully Upgraded Home Reveals Sweeping Harbour Views
Stylishly showcasing an exceptional waterfront lifestyle, a range of high-end inclusions, and breathtaking, blue-water views from every room, this stunning 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment features a free-flowing and functional floorplan for all occasions. Head downstairs to a superbly central Docklands location like no other. Simply stroll to the CBD, Southern Cross Station, and the restaurants and bars of New Quay with free city trams on your doorstep. Supremely set on the 31st floor of the popular Victoria Point tower complex, discover fabulously far-reaching, open-plan living and dining on toned timber boards, complemented by a stone-topped kitchen with a full suite of upgraded appliances. Step outside to a private astroturfed balcony showcasing a breathtaking day and night panorama, sweeping across the special tranquillity of Victoria Harbour and touching on the spectacular Melbourne Wheel and Bolte Bridge. Both window-walled bedrooms share in these same memorable views, serviced by mirrored robes and a pair of fully tiled bathrooms. One of the bedrooms features handy balcony access. Includes a double concealed laundry, secure parking plus storage cage, new floors throughout, roller blinds over openable windows, high-speed lift, video intercom entry, ducted heating/cooling, concierge, and access to a gym. This one has it all!
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for inspection details.
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Highly Sought, Rarely Found
This is a truly unique property, as an outdoor space this large is unheard of in inner city living! This stylish abode awaits discerning buyers looking for expansive open plan living, both inside and outdoors.
This 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment features your own large and private front terrace with uninterrupted parkland views. Extending around the side of the property, the connected terrace opens up to a rear private courtyard. If you love entertaining or relaxing outdoors, then this apartment is everything youre looking for & more!
A modern kitchen comprising of stainless steel European cooking appliances, a dishwasher, large stone benchtop, and ample storage space. Its generous windows provide plenty of light to the spacious dining & lounge areas with elevated views over Docklands Park.
Both bedrooms are generously sized with built in wardrobes. Master bedroom with ensuite & the second bedroom features a study nook. The central bathroom has a bath tub & shower. Separate laundry room complete with clothes dryer and ample storage. Other features include reverse cycle heating and air-conditioning, intercom entry and security system, smart-wired cable, broadband & television connections, and secure under-ground parking for one car with additional large storage cage. Access from underground car park & own elevated private secure entry from Navigation Drive.
This apartment is situated within a boutique apartment complex in the heart of the stunning Victoria Harbour precinct, offering the tranquillity of parklands and the harbour. Just a short stroll to the city, tram stops within the free tram zone, Southern Cross Station and a stones throw from Woolworths supermarket, Marvel Stadium, cafes and restaurants.

Description:
The largest two bedroom retreat in the coveted Conder
The largest two bedroom apartment in the exclusive Conder building which also comes with two bathrooms and two secure car spaces, this exclusive NewQuay precinct opportunity is one not to be missed.
An enormous 113 sqm (approx.) of space makes this a truly rare offering
Uninterrupted views of Victoria Harbour from balcony, living, and bedrooms
Immense central lounge and dining with superb light and timber floors
Generous master bedroom with ample BIRs, ensuite, and balcony access
Stone and timber kitchen with s/steel appliances overlooks the vast central zone
Immaculate bathrooms
Separate laundry room
Ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry
Storage cage
AMENITIES
The Conder complex offers residents access to an onsite building manager, pool, gym and outdoor recreation area.
LOCATION
Youre a short walk to The District Docklands which offers Hoyts Cinemas, amazing Eight Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon called The Market which will deliver an array of butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also near Marvel Stadium perfect for footy fans, Capital City Trail, leading universities, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.
